this town is full to brim
of Northern abolitionaries?

1211
01:34:41,009 --> 01:34:45,137
I am sickened, yes, but -
But now real Southern men is coming...

1212
01:34:45,221 --> 01:34:49,224
and I say "Hooray," as I am
Southern man at heart.

1213
01:34:49,309 --> 01:34:52,644
Perhaps you-you join for whiskey.

1214
01:34:52,729 --> 01:34:54,813
- I have here in office.
- [Men Shouting]

1215
01:34:54,898 --> 01:34:56,231
Whiskey?

1216
01:34:56,316 --> 01:34:57,566
Yes.

1217
01:34:59,277 --> 01:35:01,362
[Women Screaming]

1218
01:35:01,446 --> 01:35:02,905
[Gunshot]

1219
01:35:02,989 --> 01:35:04,907
- [Horse Whinnies]
- [Man] Come on! Come on!

1220
01:35:04,991 --> 01:35:07,242
Come on, peckerwood!

1221
01:35:07,327 --> 01:35:09,244
[Hoofbeats Passing]

1222
01:35:09,329 --> 01:35:11,497
- [Woman Gasps]
- [Man] I'll give you something to write about.

1223
01:35:11,581 --> 01:35:13,207
[Woman Shrieks]

1224
01:35:13,291 --> 01:35:15,751
- Goddamn lyin' bastard.
- Stay there, boy.

1225
01:35:15,835 --> 01:35:18,504
- Put this in your newspaper.
- [Screaming]

1226
01:35:18,588 --> 01:35:21,048
- [Grunts]
- [Woman Sobbing]

1227
01:35:21,132 --> 01:35:23,300
[Sobbing Continues]

1228
01:35:23,385 --> 01:35:25,344
[Glass Shattering]

1229
01:35:27,430 --> 01:35:29,973
Old man! Old man!

1230
01:35:30,975 --> 01:35:32,643
Where's your army?
[Spits]

1231
01:35:32,727 --> 01:35:36,313
Who are we to fight?
Who are we to fight?

1232
01:35:36,398 --> 01:35:38,524
- You are cowards, all!
- Send him to hell!

1233
01:35:38,608 --> 01:35:41,443
[Screaming]

1234
01:35:43,488 --> 01:35:45,697
[Woman Screaming, Indistinct]

1235
01:35:45,782 --> 01:35:47,783
- [Gunshot]
- [Screams]

1236
01:35:49,119 --> 01:35:51,036
[Sobbing]

1237
01:35:54,457 --> 01:35:57,084
- [Horse Whinnies]
- Tear it down!

1238
01:35:58,878 --> 01:36:00,921
[Men Cheering, Shouting]

1239
01:36:10,014 --> 01:36:12,724
I'll blow your head off
right here!

1240
01:36:12,809 --> 01:36:15,394
[Coughs]
Oh! You killed him!

1241
01:36:15,478 --> 01:36:18,647
Oh, let me keep his picture! No!

1242
01:36:18,731 --> 01:36:20,315
[Spits]

1243
01:36:21,401 --> 01:36:24,403
Sure, that Jim Lane -
he steal the slaves.

1244
01:36:24,487 --> 01:36:27,239
But he just sell them again
another day.

1245
01:36:27,323 --> 01:36:30,576
Me, yes, I always do what I can
for the cause.

1246
01:36:32,787 --> 01:36:35,164
It's just me and Granny Esther.

1247
01:36:37,083 --> 01:36:41,211
[Breathing Heavily]

1248
01:36:43,339 --> 01:36:45,257
[Hammer Releases]

1249
01:36:48,678 --> 01:36:51,263
[Shouting, Whooping]

1250
01:37:16,414 --> 01:37:20,042
[Cheering, Whooping]

1251
01:37:21,586 --> 01:37:25,005
- [Gunshots]
- [Cheering Continues]

1252
01:37:34,682 --> 01:37:35,933
[Whoops]

1253
01:37:51,658 --> 01:37:55,202
All right, Rocky.
Young reports Lane -

1254
01:37:56,412 --> 01:37:59,164
We had thought this would be
a real fight.

