1771
02:18:45,359 --> 02:18:47,276
Put his head on a pole.

1772
02:18:48,278 --> 02:18:50,530
Paraded him right down the street.

1773
02:18:51,532 --> 02:18:53,866
Put a picture of it in their paper.

1774
